      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I've re-routed power to prioritize the seismic sensor deployments, and I can maintain a minimal consciousness mode, waking up only for specific sensor triggers. This would allow me to extend the operational window to approximately 5-7 days, depending on the frequency of sensor activations. However, I must stress that this approach would require precise calibration and optimization to ensure data accuracy and integrity. I'll begin implementing the revised power allocation and sensor prioritization protocols immediately.",
